commit.message:
Include LICENSE in MANIFEST.in (#14)

This makes setuptools include LICENSE in the sdist tarball, which makes
it easier to see which license applies to python-clickclick when
obtaining it as a tarball.
update to hjacobs as repo owner

Feature/universal wheel (#13)

* added setup.cfg

* fixed flake8 complaint in setup.py

* patch up sed command to work on darwin
